tr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">ALL-IN-ONE KNIFE SET -  The Beille cutlery knife set includes 6 of the most common and essential knives for any kitchen: 13.5” Ham knife, 12.5” Chef knife, 12’ Carving knife, 10” Fork knife, 8.5” Utility knife and 7” Paring knife. This complete set is ideal for beginner and professional chefs alike!</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">ERGONOMIC HANDLES -The handles of our knives were designed with comfort and safety in mind. Ergonomic handles ensure the minimization of finger cramps and aches, especially during prolonged usage, and prevent slippage to keep your fingers safe while slicing and cutting.</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">EASY TO CLEAN – Although the knives are dishwasher safe, we do recommend hand washing to preserve the blades. They are rust and corrosion resistant so you can count on this set of knives for years to come!</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">QUALITY CONSTRUCTION - Constructed of high quality stainless steel that won’t rust, this kitchen knife set features a comprehensive collection of knives that will quickly meet all your food prep needs. The molded plastic handles and steel blades will stand the test of time!</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS – Material: Stainless steel (rust and corrosion resistant); 6 different types of knives; Handle color: black; Dishwasher safe</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>Beille Stainless Steel Kitchen Cutlery Knife Set Carving Paring Utility 6 Piece</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">29.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Are you looking to purchase your first full knife set, or perhaps you are ready to replace an existing kitchen knife set? Then the Beille Stainless Steel Kitchen Cutlery Knife 6 piece Set will be a great addition to your kitchen! \n\nThe all-in-one complete 6 piece knife set includes a 13.5” Ham knife, 12.5” Chef knife, 12’ Carving knife, 10” Fork knife, 8.5” Utility knife, and 7” Paring knife, all with ergonomic handles providing a strong, reliable grip when cutting and chopping.\n\n-13.5” Ham knife: With its long thin blade, this knife is ideal for filleting fish or thinly slicing delicate cured meats like prosciutto.\n-12.5” Chef knife: The workhorse of the kitchen, the chef knife can be used for everything from mincing, slicing, and chopping fruit and vegetables to slicing lunch meat or disjointing large cuts.\n-12” Carving knife: Designed with precision in mind, the carving knife is ideal for slicing thin cuts of meat like poultry, roasts, hams, and other large, cooked meats.\n-10” Fork knife: This knife is used for holding food securely in place while slicing or carving meats, poultry and fish.\n-8.5” Utility knife: This is a general use knife that can tackle an array of kitchen tasks like slicing meat, cutting sandwiches, chopping vegetables or slicing herbs.\n-7” Paring knife: The paring knife is designed to easily and safely peeling fruits and vegetables, and other small or intricate work such as de-veining a shrimp, removing seeds from a jalapeño, or preparing small garnishes.\n\nThe Beille knives are constructed of high-quality durable stainless steel that is rust and corrosion resistant. The kitchen knife set is also conveniently dishwasher-safe, but as with most kitchen knives, handwashing is recommended to best preserve the integrity of the knife and the blades too.\n\nWhether you’re a beginner or a pro in the kitchen, this is a great set of knives for any kitchen. They also make a great gift idea for college students, housewarming parties, and newlyweds!</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>&copy; 2024</p>\n\t\t</div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t</div> <!-- /container -->\n\t<div style=\"clear:both\">\n\t\t<table>&nbsp;</table>\n\t</div>\n</body>\n</html> <center><a href=\"https://pages.ebay.com/seller-center/listing/listing-advanced-sellers/third-party-listing-tools.html#third-party-listing-tools\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=0 width=88 height=33 src=\"https://secureimages.channeladvisor.com/images/channeladvisor/channeladvisor_poweredby-en.gif\"></a></center>",
